      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of peerless quality, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen represents the benchmark for its class, exhibiting an immaculate exterior finish paired with a pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically flawless and documented with a comprehensive service history, this motorcar offers the discerning enthusiast a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-grade example. Every detail, from the factory-correct paint depth to the supple leather upholstery, confirms its status as a collector-grade acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
