    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been pampered like royalty\u2014always garage-kept, spotless inside and out, and honestly, you won't find a single blemish anywhere. It drives like a dream and has been loved every single mile. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this gem as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
