    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the critical dual-VANOS system and rod bearings recently serviced for preventative longevity. The chassis integrity is preserved via a reinforced rear subframe, while the 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and variable M differential lock provide an unfiltered connection to the tarmac. Finished in original factory paint with a pristine interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s high-revving engineering, free of any forced induction or electronic interference.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
